            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛CEO：正密切關注私人信貸市場泡沫跡象",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高盛CEO：正密切關注私人信貸市場泡沫跡象\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Rcj92dlvQqCidd3E3rFp0A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/7d035340-a8f1-11f0-ad7e-0a9dce6f5dee\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高盛CEO：正密切關注私人信貸市場泡沫跡象</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
